th%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22retro%20hq%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c3456832af4d666ef7be54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221622%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERetro%20Biosciences%20sits%20in%20a%20%26quot%3BSilicon%20Valley%26quot%3B%20suburb%20north%20of%20San%20Francisco.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Winokur%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBetts-LaCroix%20assures%20me%20that%20Retro%20is%20in%20%26quot%3Bhardcore%20preclinical%20mode.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERTR242%20is%20one%20of%20at%20least%20three%20big%20ideas%20the%20company%20is%20currently%20betting%20on%20to%20reverse%20aging.%20All%20of%20Retro's%20big%20bets%20share%20the%20goal%20of%20taking%20some%20aspect%20of%20our%20biology%20%26quot%3Bback%20to%20essentially%20a%20younger%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20Betts-LaCroix%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetro's%20been%20vocal%20about%20its%20ultimate%20goal%3A%20to%20add%2010%20extra%2C%20healthy%20years%20to%20human%20lifespan.%20They're%20not%20necessarily%20saying%20US%20life%20expectancy%20would%20ramp%20up%20to%2088%20from%2078.%20Rather%2C%20they're%20trying%20to%20create%20novel%20treatments%20that%20keep%20people%20feeling%20healthy%2C%20alert%2C%20and%20vibrant%20right%20until%20their%20very%20last%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20the%20Alzheimer's%20drug%2C%20Retro%20is%20in%20the%20preclinical%20development%20stage%20for%20a%20treatment%20for%20blood%20diseases%20like%20leukemia%2C%20which%20involves%20making%20fresh%20blood%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstem-cell-injections-knee-joints-longevity-wellness-industry-bryan-johnson-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estem%20cells%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20patients%20using%20their%20own%20cells%20as%20a%20starting%20point%20(RTR890)%2C%20plus%20a%20stem%20cell-derived%20therapy%20for%20treating%20diseases%20of%20the%20central%20nervous%20system%20(RTR888).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experimental%20memory%20pill%20works%20by%20