%20its%20old%20airport%20in%20Doha%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Einto%20an%20exclusive%20hub%2C%20catering%20to%20the%20royal%20family%2C%20government%20officials%2C%20and%20the%20uber-wealthy%20traveling%20in%20private%20jets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decor%20has%20a%201960s%20%26quot%3BMad%20Men%26quot%3B%20vibe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20notice%20any%20restaurants%2C%20shops%2C%20or%20lounges%20like%20you'd%20see%20in%20a%20typical%20airport.%20It%20was%20also%20mostly%20empty%3B%20I%20didn't%20see%20many%20other%20passengers%20waiting%20for%20their%20flights.%20But%20that's%20likely%20because%20private%20jet%20customers%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20through%20security%20cues%20or%20wait%20in%20line%20to%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20plane%20was%20waiting%20on%20the%20tarmac%2C%20where%20the%20temperature%20was%20about%20108%20degrees%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Qatar%20Executive%20plane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b9c162f9db348adc0ad4d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20pilot%20greeted%20us%20outside%20the%20plane.%3Cp%3EMark%20Adam%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20took%20a%20media%20tour%20on%20one%20of%20Qatar%20Executive's%20latest%20planes%3A%20the%20Gulfstream%20G700.%20A%20one-way%20flight%20on%20this%20jet%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Doha%20can%20cost%20up%20to%20%24300%2C000%2C%20which%20is%20about%2030%20times%20more%20expensive%20than%20flying%20on%20Qatar%20Airways'%20business%20class%2C%20the%20Qsuite%2C%20on%20the%20same%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20stayed%20on%20the%20tarmac%20during%20our%20tour%20to%20avoid%20adding%20carbon%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20soon%20as%20I%20walked%20in%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20this%20was%20definitely%20better%20than%20first%20class%20or%20the%20Qsuite%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20Qatar%20Executive's%20private%20jet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b9be80f9db348adc0ad456%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221546%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20G700%20boasts%20one%20of%20the%20most%20spacious%20private%20jet%20cabins.%3Cp%3EMark%20Adam%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20strolled%20through%20this%20%2480%20million%20plane%2C%20my%20videographer%20and%20I%20were%20a%20little%20afraid%20that%20we%20would%20scratch%20the%20brand-new%20leather%20interiors%20and%20panels%20that%20were%20customized%20to%20reflect%20Qatar%20Executive's%20branding%20and%20aesthetic.%20The%20plane%20also%20smelled%20like%20a%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehigh-end%20leather%20handbag%20store.%20Everything%20seemed%20too%20nice%20to%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20made%20a%20beeline%20for%20the%20bedroom%20suite%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222888%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bed%20on%20Qatar%20Executive%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b9c3dc32af4d666ef73f96%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221510%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20private%20bedroom%20with%20a%20double%20bed%20steals%20the%20show.%3Cp%3EMark%20Adam%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20private%20jet's%20standout%20features%20is%20the%20spacious%20bedroom%20suite%20at%20the%20back%2C%20which%20maximizes%20privacy%20and%C2%A0allows%20flight%20attendants%20to%20move%20around%C2%A0the%20rest%20of%20the%20plane.%20While%20most%20first-class%20cabins%20turn%20seats%20into%20beds%2C%20the%20bedroom%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehad%20a%20double%20bed%20with%20a%20mattress%20and%20storage%20space%20underneath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20pilots%20told%20me%20that%20this%20plane%20flies%20at%2090%25%20the%20speed%20of%20sound%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222886%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pilots%20on%20Qatar%20Executive%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b9cff4f9db348adc0ad738%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221548%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20pilots%20pointed%20out%20features%20that%20make%20flying%20more%20comfortable.%3Cp%3EMark%20Adam%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pilots%2C%20who%20were%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Fiji%2C%20told%20me%20that%20this%20Gulfstream%20has%20surprising%20benefits.%20It's%20faster%20than%20a%20typical%20commercial%20airliner%2C%C2%A0and%20it%20can%20fly%2010%2C000%20feet%20higher%2C%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%2051%2C000%20feet.%20That%20means%20it%20can%20avoid%20other%20air%20traffic%20and%20certain%20weather%20patterns%20that%20can%20cause%20turbulence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHaving%20custom%20meals%20at%20any%20time%20is%20definitely%20a%20perk%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222866%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Qatar%20food%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b9def832af4d666ef7442e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221522%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20food%20on-board%20can%20be%20customized%20to%20your%20needs.%3Cp%3EMark%20Adam%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sampled%20Qatar%20Executive's%20high%20tea%2C%20which%20included%20caviar%2C%20chicken%20tikka%20sandwiches%2C%20and%20macarons.%20The%20flight%20attendant%20told%20me%20that%20customers%20can%20order%20from%20local%20bakeries%20or%20restaurants%2C%20and%20a%20concierge%20service%20will%20buy%20those%20items%20and%20serve%20them%20on%20board.%20The%20treats%20I%20feasted%20on%20were%20prepared%20at%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecompany's%20in-house%20catering%20kitchen%20in%20Doha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20went%20behind%20the%20scenes%20at%20the%20catering%20facility%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222248%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Qatar%20Airways%20catering%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b9d771f9db348adc0ad88d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQatar's%20catering%20facility%20has%20won%20several%20industry%20awards.%3Cp%3EMark%20Adam%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20day%20earlier%2C%20I%20visited%20the%20airline's%20catering%20hub%20near%20the%20airport%2C%20where%20chefs%20prepare%20200%2C000%20meals%20a%20day%20from%20scratch.%20The%20kitchens%20serve%20Qatar%20Airways%2C%20its%20partner%20airlines%2C%20airport%20lounges%2C%20and%20private%20flights%20on%20Qatar%20Executive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESome%20of%20these%20treats%20were%20a%20work%20of%20art%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222293%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Qatar%20food%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bad2b332af4d666ef74edb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221153%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresentation%20was%20a%20big%20part%20of%20the%20private%20flying%20experience.%3Cp%3EMark%20Adam%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20flies%20economy%2C%20I%20was%20blown%20away%20by%20how%20beautiful%20and%20delicious%20Qatar%20Executive's%20meals%20were.%20The%20crew%20has%20an%20oven%2C%20microwave%2C%20and%20refrigerator%20on%20board%20to%20keep%20things%20fresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20found%20myself%20nerding%20out%20about%20the%20subtle%20high-tech%20touches%20like%20this%20door%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222862%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bedroom%20door%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b9c84332af4d666ef74041%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221578%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bedroom%20door%20is%20specially%20designed%20to%20maximize%20privacy.%3Cp%3EMark%20Adam%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20electronically%20controlled%20doors%20on%20the%20plane%20move%20up%20and%20down%20instead%20of%20sideways%2C%20so%20they%20can%20close%20completely%2C%20allowing%20for%20more%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEven%20