-pwc-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsultant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20difficult%2C%20is%20a%20linear%20track%20for%20many%20who%20land%20in%20the%20industry.%20Big%20firms%20head%20to%20schools%20and%20pluck%20freshly%20minted%20MBAs%20to%20join%20their%20ranks.%20After%20years%20of%20mentorship%2C%20long%20hours%2C%20and%20loads%20of%20hard%20work%2C%20you%20might%20eventually%20become%20a%20partner%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prestigious%20titles%20a%20consultant%20could%20aspire%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20dream%20might%20be%20creeping%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20younger%20people%20trying%20to%20break%20into%20the%20industry%2C%20which%20looks%20to%20be%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20a%20big%20shift%20as%20firms%20trim%20their%20ranks%2C%20double%20down%20on%20AI%2C%20and%20tighten%20performance%20standards%20across%20the%20career%20ladder%2C%20industry%20analysts%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20is%20exactly%20sure%20how%20it%20will%20play%20out%2C%20as%20much%20of%20the%20future%20will%20depend%20on%20where%20the%20economy%20goes%20and%20how%20quickly%20AI%20is%20adopted.%20But%20the%20end%20result%20could%20look%20something%20like%20a%20reshaping%20of%20the%20profession%2C%20with%20fewer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-ai-cut-entry-level-law-finance-consulting-jobs-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eentry-level%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20senior%20roles%E2%80%94something%20that%20could%20make%20it%20more%20challenging%20for%20young%20people%20in%20the%20field%20trying%20to%20rise%20through%20the%20ranks%2C%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20restructuring%20is%20already%20faintly%20visible%20in%20the%20numbers.%20According%20to%20Revelio%20Labs%2C%20a%20workforce%20intelligence%20firm%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flanding-dream-jobs-tech-consulting-banking-are-harder-than-ever-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejob%20postings%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20cons