20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bcg.com%2Fpress%2Fbcg-announces-re-election-of-chief-executive-officer-christoph-schweizer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20its%20growth%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERon%20Kermisch%2C%20a%20senior%20partner%20and%20the%20global%20head%20of%20talent%20acquisition%20at%20Bain%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20firm%20grew%20its%20summer%20MBA%20program%20in%20North%20America%20by%2020%25%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20just%20absorbing%20all%20the%20people%20who%20we%20had%20brought%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Kermisch%20said%20of%20the%20years%20following%20the%20pandemic.%20%26quot%3BBut%20now%20we've%20worked%20our%20way%20through%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20analysts%20who%20closely%20follow%20the%20industry%20are%20skeptical%20that%20numbers%20will%20increase%20meaningfully%20in%20the%20future.%20IBISWorld%20estimates%20that%20hiring%20growth%20in%20the%20broader%20category%20of%20management%20consulting%20will%20slow%20to%201.4%25%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade%2C%20its%20slowest%20pace%20since%20at%20least%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FXWV0z%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22458%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20PR%20positioning%2C%26quot%3B%20Mian%20said%20of%20companies%20talking%20about%20ramping%20up%20hiring.%26quot%3BBecause%20you%20still%20want%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20aspirational%20brand%20for%20top%20talent.%20And%20if%20you%20start%20to%20talk%20about%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-career-options-alternatives-harvard-advisor-graduate-how-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eentry-level%20hiring%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20going%20to%20decrease%20in%20the%20future%2C%20then%20some%20of%20this%20top%20up-and-coming%20talent%20isn't%20going%20to%20consider%20you%20as%20a%20potential%20employer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we're%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20see%20a%20very%20gradual%20culling%20of%20the%20herd%20in%20certain%20practice%20areas%20at%20certain%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20speculating%20that%20the%20shift%20could%20stretch%20on%20for%20as%20long%20as%20a%20decade%20before%20stabilizing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETom%20Rodenhauser%2C%20a%20consulting%20analyst%20and%20the%20managing%20partner%20at%20Kennedy%20Intelligence%2C%20also%20believes%20the%20decline%20in%20strategy%20consulting%20is%20more%20secular%20than%20cyclical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20different%20this%20time%20around%20is%20this%20isn't%20a%20cycle%20that's%20going%20to%20change%20dramatically.%20There%20isn't%20going%20to%20be%20this%20huge%20surge%20and%20everyone's%20going%20to%20go%20back%20to%20business%20as%20usual.%20There's%20a%20fundamental%20shift%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220285905e-10a4-4e7b-83db-fbc4ed437599%5C%22%3ENew%20structure%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMian%20thinks%20the%20industry%20is%20shifting%20away%20from%20the%20pyramid%20model%20%E2%80%94%20one%20with%20a%20fat%20base%20and%20a%20skinny%20top-tier%20%E2%80%94%20to%20one%20with%20a%20larger%20middle%20that%20is%20lean%20on%20the%20entry-%20and%20senior-level%20workers.%20He%20sees%20a%20few%20reasons%20for%20the%20change%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemand%20is%20shifting.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20big%20strategy%20consulting%20firms%20overhired%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20progress%20made%20in%20terms%20of%20figuring%20out%20the%20right%20strategy%20for%20businesses.%20That%20means%20strategy%20consultants%20are%20less%20in%20demand%2C%20Mian%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWanting%20more%20expertise.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHiring%20in%20more%20specialized%20areas%20of%20consulting%2C%20like%20tech%20consulting%2C%20has%20increased%20in%20recent%20years.%20That%20reflects%20the%20fact%20that%20consulting%20firms%20are%20now%20looking%20for%20more%20experience%2C%20or%20those%20who%20have%20knowledge%20in%20a%20specific%20field%2C%20Mian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20firms%20are%20emphasizing%20experience%20and%20expertise%20more%20than%20they%20ever%20have%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%2C%20you%20still%20might%20be%20hiring%20nine%20or%2010%20people%20in%20a%20given%20office%20in%20a%20given%20year%2C%20but%20now%20instead%20of%20all%2010%20of%20them%20being%20undergrad%20analysts%2C%20maybe%20only%20half%20of%20them%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELike%20many%20employers%2C%20consultancies%20have%20been%20cutting%20costs%20and%20leaning%20toward%20artificial%20intelligence.%20Mian%20says%20that%20could%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20entry-level%20hiring%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Revelio%20analysis%20found%20that%20consulting%20was%20one%20of%20the%20industries%20most%20exposed%20to%20AI%2C%20with%2045%25%20of%20activities%20that%20could%20be%20performed%20using%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FbhwKL%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22328%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20could%20that%20cut%20down%20on%20analyst%20hiring%20in%20the%20future%3F%20Absolutely%2C%26quot%3B%20Mian%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20believed%20junior%20talent%20was%20most%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20narrower%20partner%20track.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPerformance%20standards%20are%20being%20raised%20at%20top%20firms%2C%20Mian%20said%2C%20citing%20conversations%20with%20people%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20firms%20are%20promoting%20fewer%20partners%20than%20they%20were%20in%20the%20past.%20McKinsey%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20reportedly%20minted%20around%20200%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-promotes-smallest-partner-class-years-consulting-slowdown-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epartners%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024%2C%20about%20half%20the%20number%20of%20new%20partners%20it%20minted%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeloitte's%20UK%20arm%20promoted%2060%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeloitte-uk-partner-promotions-lower-than-last-year-consulting-slowdown-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epartners%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%2C%20down%2025%25%20from%20last%20year's%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKermisch%20said%20Bain%20had%20%26quot%3Brefined%26quot%3B%20its%20recruiting%20process%20and%20was%20now%20searching%20for%20specific%20traits%20among%20its%20pool%20of%20potential%20hires.%20The%20company%20is%20seeking%20those%20who%20have%20EQ%E2%80%94which%20will%20allow%20consultants%20to%20work%20effectively%20with%20clients%E2%80%94and%20what%20he%20calls%20%26quot%3Btechnical%20curiosity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20people%20to%20constantly%20be%20thinking%2C%20'How%20can%20I%20apply%20AI%20here%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20people%20whose%20natural%20disposition%20is%20to%20think%20that%20way%20first%2C%20so%20they%20can%20get%20that%20work%20done%20more%20quickly%2C%20more%20creatively%20than%20they%20would%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKermisch%20said%20he%20wasn't%20sure%20if%20it%20was%20now%20more%20difficult%20for%20consultants%20across%20the%20industry%20to%20become%20partners.%20He%20believes%20that%20large%20employers%20in%20the%20space%20will%20stick%20to%20the%20pyramid%20model%2C%20but%20he%20said%20it%20was%20possible%20t