rs.%20But%20I%20know%20he%20has%20somewhere%20to%20be%3B%20I%E2%80%99m%20keeping%20a%20hundred%20and%20fifty%20of%20his%20jungle%20friends%20waiting%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20one%20last%20question%20before%20you%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20say%2C%20unable%20to%20stop%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20do%20you%20see%20in%20them%20that%20connects%20you%20to%20them%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20near%20persons%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20them%20in%20terms%20of%20conscience%2C%20memory%2C%20and%20intellect.%20They%20are%20very%20similar%20to%20us.%20They%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20understand%20my%20words%20or%20my%20language.%20But%20they%20understand%20me%20in%20other%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20before%20he%20concludes%20our%20conversation%20to%20head%20to%20the%20place%20where%20he%20feels%20most%20at%20home%20%E2%80%94%20amid%20the%20elephants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wildlife-biodiversity.com%2Findex.php%2Fjwb%2Farticle%2Fdownload%2F223%2F310%2F1074%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElephant%20Corridor%20loss%20due%20to%20anthropogenic%20stress%20%E2%80%93%20a%20study%20of%20change%20in%20forest%20cover%20using%20satellite%20data%20in%20the%20Sonitpur%20District%2C%20Assam%2C%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%3A%20by%20Journal%20of%20Wildlife%20and%20Biodiversity%2C%20Published%20on%207%20June%202022.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifaw.org%2Finternational%2Fjournal%2Fhuman-elephant-conflict-major-threat%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHuman-elephant%20conflict%3A%20What%20it%20is%20and%20why%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20major%20